{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5a8a6ed5fe","title":"给邹普勋的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"24cf1aebef","index":0,"year":1953,"month":7,"day":11,"articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"c86637435f","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邹普勋，毛泽东少年时的私垫同学和邻居。"},{"id":"529a10603d","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李激清，毛泽东少年时的老师，大革命时期曾协助毛泽东在广州办过《政治周报》。新中国成立后曾任湖南省文史研究馆馆员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d2d0570725","type":"title","text":"给邹普勋的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"},{"id":"c86637435f","type":"paragraph","text":"普勋兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"},{"id":"529a10603d","type":"paragraph","text":"七月一日的信收到。你的生活提高一些，甚感，为你庆贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"},{"id":"0a70bb4148","type":"paragraph","text":"秋收以后，如你愿意来北京一游，可以借李激清先生一道来京住个把月。李渐清先生去年来信想来北京一次，但不知他今年尚有此种兴趣否，他的身体能出远门否？","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"},{"id":"5d7a7838bf","type":"subtitle","text":"顺祝","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"},{"id":"068f6296a1","type":"paragraph","text":"安吉","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"},{"id":"875bc29d13","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a6ed5fe"},{"id":"60590a7388","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十一日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"5a8a